Package: isp-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php-cli, php-spojenet-abraflexi (>= 3.4), php-vitexsoftware-abraflexi-bricks
Description: ISP tools for AbraFlexi-based internet access management
 Utilities for managing internet customer disconnection/reconnection
 based on AbraFlexi invoice status and customer labels.
 .
 Includes: abraflexi-mark-defaulters (bridge UPOMINKA3 → ODPOJENO),
 blocknet (disconnect overdue internet customers),
 unblocknet (reconnect cleared customers).

Package: multiflexi-isp-tools
Architecture: all
Section: web
Priority: optional
Depends: multiflexi-cli, isp-tools
Description: Add ISP Tools to MultiFlexi
 Install or update MultiFlexi application JSON definitions for
 ISP Tools (mark-defaulters, blocknet, unblocknet) into MultiFlexi.
